prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover. A humorous and lighthearted watercolor illustration of Lao Lao and Jordan on a sunny beach. The scene is full of comedic action. Jordan is comically tangled up in a giant, brightly colored kite string, looking surprised and laughing as the kite soars high above. Lao Lao, holding a celebratory birthday drink with a little umbrella, is laughing heartily at his predicament. They are both transformed into charming cartoon versions of themselves, wearing the same outfits from the reference photo (Lao Lao in a light blue sweatshirt and black pants, Jordan in a tan hoodie and dark pants, logos omitted). The beach is whimsical, with sandcastles shaped like birthday cakes and crabs wearing tiny party hats scuttling by. The ocean is a beautiful blend of turquoise and blue watercolor washes, with gentle waves lapping the shore. In the center of the image, written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!". Flat 2D artwork, soft edges, vibrant watercolor style.
